Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.56,0:01:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 这东西可真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.99,0:01:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓的dol-pli啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.52,0:01:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,drill purine?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs18\pos(340,328)}idol-appli
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.27,0:01:50.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做偶像程序
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电脑世界的换装玩偶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这年代真是无处不进化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.90,0:01:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您不知道还排队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.20,0:01:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.44,0:02:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我去买那个最新发售的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.95,0:02:02.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么来着
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.72,0:02:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.11,0:02:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.26,0:02:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌曲  歌曲  歌曲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.07,0:02:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是歌曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.92,0:02:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌曲啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.96,0:02:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新歌和新的声音数据
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.59,0:02:13.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全区别与以前的主唱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.90,0:02:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且和真正的活人的声音一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.78,0:02:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听了试听觉得真的很厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.54,0:02:22.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  歌很好听  很像夜长公主的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真够险的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.26,0:02:25.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜长公主是危险领域啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.20,0:02:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网上也有曲子和歌词已经偷跑的传言…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.02,0:02:37.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.49,0:02:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原定在今天发售的偶像程序的追加数据被禁止发售了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.07,0:02:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.43,0:02:47.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢耍我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.78,0:02:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道我们等多久了吗！？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.66,0:02:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说对不起能解决问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.72,0:02:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被禁止发售是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.27,0:02:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被迫中止的吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\frz-90\an5\bord0\fn@宋体\b1\fs13\c&HFFFFFF&\move(482,165,496,165,0,420)\clip(488,54,549,247)}非法软件贩卖者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.86,0:02:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  我们这边也头疼着呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:02:58.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.86,0:03:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.02,0:03:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有认证的出租车
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.63,0:03:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是坐了那辆黑车的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.63,0:03:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在跟司机说她忘记带重要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.31,0:03:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还有别的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能麻烦您帮我去送一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.57,0:03:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托您了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司机就照她所说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.49,0:03:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去她指定的地方拿东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个地方就是横滨投资家长田久子小姐家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长田家的门卫那里的确如女人所说有寄放的行李箱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.21,0:03:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司机在途中猜测里面的会是金银财宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.62,0:03:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打开行李来确认  结果发现
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.57,0:03:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面装着房子的主人  长田久子小姐自己的尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\an5\bord0.3\be3\3a&H3C\fn@宋体\b1\fs13\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H000000&\move(70,178,82,178,0,340)\clip(76,95,131,348)}投资家 被害人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.81,0:03:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还真有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.03,0:03:55.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎山  爸爸不过只是收集消息的人而非侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系  我也颇有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:02.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么多谜团的案件也只能靠会长帮助我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.75,0:04:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\an5\bord0\fn@宋体\b1\fs13\c&H000000&\clip(29,60,277,280)\move(24,154,38,154,0,480)}海胜麟六之女  帮其处理家务
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:07.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人难道不是那个乘坐黑车的女人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.59,0:04:10.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行李箱是另外一个男人寄放的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.84,0:04:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\an5\bord0\fn@宋体\b1\fs12\c&HFFFFFF&\move(484,159,498,159,0,420)\clip(492,58,620,275)}检察厅 联合调查部 检察官
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.73,0:04:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便条纸上写着
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.30,0:04:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs14\bord1\fad(0,300)}感冒了没法说话\N麻烦您帮我把这个行李箱寄放在这里\N没多久就会有黑车来取\N麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没多久就会有黑车来取  希望能寄放一会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.16,0:04:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,门卫本来想着要拒绝…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想长田久子小姐是在外被杀害的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.44,0:04:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那个犯人要特意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把放了长田小姐尸体的行李箱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.48,0:04:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寄放在长田小姐她本人家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)\an5\bord0\b1\fs13\c&H000000&\fn宋体\move(186,142,198,142,0,440)\clip(192,114,296,265)}J\NJ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.86,0:04:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,600)\an5\bord0\b1\fs13\c&H000000&\fn@宋体\frz-90\move(186,183,198,183,0,440)\clip(192,114,296,265)}系统会长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.69,0:04:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 他和打黑车的女人之间究竟是什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 事情的真相是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.29,0:04:43.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌疑犯是饮食店经营人  荒卷敏司  47岁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.03,0:04:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被害人长田久子丧夫之后的情人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那位荒卷先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说有比较奇怪的爱好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒卷先生有女装癖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.44,0:05:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  寄放行李箱的那个男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘坐黑车的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是荒卷变装而成的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.87,0:05:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让人以为是两个人一起犯案
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.32,0:05:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澄清自己才是荒卷的真正目的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.05,0:05:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在  我们正在全力追踪荒卷的行迹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\an5\bord0\fn@宋体\b1\fs12\c&H000000&\clip(492,174,582,251)\move(487,207,499,207,0,420)}侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\an5\bord0\fn@宋体\b1\fs12\c&H000000&\clip(93,148,201,253)\move(88,193,98,193,0,420)}助理侦探
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.05,0:05:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎么走
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不能像小船那样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.97,0:05:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.26,0:05:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好听的声音所以  不小心就想录下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\an5\bord0\fn@宋体\b1\fs12\move(487,190,498,190,0,420)\clip(492,58,620,275)\c&H000000&}被害人之女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.52,0:05:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是侦探吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.77,0:05:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想找到杀害你母亲的犯人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:06:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  前两天已经由海胜麟六推理得出…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.70,0:06:05.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荒卷叔叔不可能是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是下落不明了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我母亲很早以前就一直被某个人恐吓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个月都往品川的饭店寄钱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,品川的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.87,0:06:22.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你帮我把行李箱带到品川的饭店去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.44,0:06:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这相当可疑啊新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.13,0:06:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  究竟是谁恐吓的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:32.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是…夜长公主的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.12,0:06:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是犯人肯定是别人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.31,0:06:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就请交给这位战败侦探结城新十郎吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市的灯光非常美丽  横滨…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.47,0:06:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20}这是刚刚那首歌吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我奶奶教我唱的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.56,0:07:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说在奶奶的国家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电视和收音机里都不能放日语歌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.18,0:07:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这首歌虽然是日语却很受欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.29,0:07:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都偷偷的唱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得歌曲的力量大到无法想象呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.14,0:07:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你难道  想当歌手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  曾一度以为自己不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我还是觉得不能放弃自己的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.34,0:07:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为梦想一定会实现么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦  新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假定犯人是荒卷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么他为什么特意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.99,0:07:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把行李箱放回被害人的家里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.25,0:07:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.54,0:07:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜长公主  夜长…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,网上关于夜长公主的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.62,0:08:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,图像和声音已经全部被和谐了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.54,0:08:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人上传相关数据
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.78,0:08:09.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就会以「新情报扩散防止法」逮捕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.30,0:08:12.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会是真不知道夜长公主吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我之前不在日本嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.43,0:08:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是转换成偶像程序的文件
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs20\fad(800,800)\an8}（瓦尔哈拉处女丘）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.69,0:08:42.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界啊  你要苏醒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.49,0:08:49.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,临近日出  尽头都染成了美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.54,0:08:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映照……
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还声称国民偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.26,0:09:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争之后电视上每天都播这首歌
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要打倒恐怖袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.05,0:09:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要大规模动兵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.74,0:09:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只因大力支持舆论
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战后的政府禁止了这首歌的放出
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3人+1是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.88,0:09:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜长公主3+1
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有她们的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.56,0:09:28.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.59,0:09:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说夜长公主本来是有4个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是其中一个人在初次登台之前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.43,0:09:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在东京首次的袭击中牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.52,0:09:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是世称的12.23恐怖事件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.07,0:09:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而她的死前景象
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.47,0:09:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都记录在了这台监控录像里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.62,0:09:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恵理她没有死
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她永远和我们在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.71,0:09:54.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们四个人在一起才是夜长公主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.96,0:09:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们绝对不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.73,0:09:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会输
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.02,0:10:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要夺回我们的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请听听我们的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次演出让她们一夜成名
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.09,0:10:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事前被录下来的恵理的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:10.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也被直接用于演出
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.16,0:10:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将站起的你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:15.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道的其一切
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前方指引着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那坠落折断的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是世称的恵理之声
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.98,0:10:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在夜长公主解散以后
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.36,0:10:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\an5\bord0\fn@宋体\b1\fs13\c&H000000&\move(69,182,82,182,0,400)\clip(74,60,277,288)}中桥橙香之兄
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.68,0:10:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹她有想过单飞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.87,0:10:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但由于长田小姐的反对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长田小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是长田久子小姐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.23,0:10:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\bord0.3\be3\3a&H4f\fn@宋体\b1\fs12\3c&H000000&\c&Hffffff&\clip(492,42,577,249)\move(487,197,499,197,0,280)}3\N+\N1
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\an5\bord0.3\be3\3a&H4f\fn@宋体\b1\fs12\3c&H000000&\c&Hffffff&\clip(492,42,577,249)\move(487,173,499,173,0,280)}原?夜长公主\h\h\h成员
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.71,0:10:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长田久子小姐和夜长公主是什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.66,0:10:59.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  她是事务所的社长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是夜长公主的创始人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.42,0:11:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人都已经到了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜长  夜长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:14.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:22.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是梦乃小姐和公美小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.48,0:11:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜长  夜长
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.46,0:11:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\bord0\fn@宋体\b1\fs12\3c&H000000&\1c&H000000&\move(240,193,253,193,0,430)\clip(245,72,304,273)\fad(0,600)}3\N+\N1
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.40,0:11:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\an5\bord0\fn@宋体\b1\fs12\3c&H000000&\c&H000000&\clip(245,72,304,273)\move(240,170,253,170,0,430)\fad(0,600)}原?夜长公主\h\h\h成员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.65,0:11:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\bord0\fn@宋体\b1\fs12\3c&H000000&\1c&H000000&\move(521,193,534,193,0,430)\fad(0,600)\clip(526,83,631,299)}3\N+\N1
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.65,0:11:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\an5\bord0\fn@宋体\b1\fs12\3c&H000000&\c&H000000&\move(521,170,534,170,0,430)\fad(0,600)\clip(526,83,631,299)}原?夜长公主\h\h\h成员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您找我是因为长田小姐的案件
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来您已经知道犯人是谁了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.49,0:11:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说两位每个月都会和被害人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.16,0:11:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约在此处见一次面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.63,0:11:34.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.55,0:11:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据我调查
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.90,0:11:37.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被害者在被杀害前正受到不明人士的恐吓威胁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.78,0:11:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.04,0:11:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是社长长田小姐她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.33,0:11:43.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为担心而给我们的生活费
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.01,0:11:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐姐  你如果不开口说话我还以为你是男的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.75,0:11:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说搬运长田久子的尸体的人是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.72,0:11:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身份不明的男人和女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.28,0:11:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怀疑是我们杀害了社长吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.62,0:11:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.17,0:12:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  当然不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果社长死了我们都不知道该怎么生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:10.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乍看之下是男女共犯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,品川旅馆与长田久子也甚有渊源
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.11,0:12:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人想设计让我们认为你们就是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人…？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如这个小恵理的幽灵之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.77,0:12:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恵理已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死于12.23恐怖袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.32,0:12:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梦乃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.49,0:12:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.28,0:12:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经忍不住了  新十郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.12,0:12:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再装了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.00,0:12:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早就已经察觉真相所在了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.83,0:12:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是动机不纯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.71,0:12:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就让我来明确动机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.80,0:13:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说过要让我看看真正的人类吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让我看看人类真实的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.14,0:13:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是真相还没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.21,0:13:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少骗我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.37,0:13:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要得到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想保护什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新十郎真是温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那个孩子可就惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.42,0:13:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是自怜自哀的话什么也不会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.00,0:13:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我  该怎么提问才好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.55,0:13:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第4位夜长公主的真实身份
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.03,0:13:54.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事不能告诉任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.93,0:13:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有让对方必须回答自己一个问题的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.05,0:14:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第4位夜长公主到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:11.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜长公主本是三人组合
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.43,0:14:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死于恐怖袭击的安西恵理呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.85,0:14:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个录像是决定首次登台演出的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.44,0:14:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长田小姐带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.56,0:14:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后她说让那个孩子作为我们已去世的成员出现
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.20,0:14:38.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连她的歌声都被录制在磁带中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.11,0:14:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恵理这个人我们连见都没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是无法拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.08,0:14:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说只要接受要求我们就能红
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.64,0:14:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争结束后夜长公主解散
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:14:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于恵理要绝对保密
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果泄露半点的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:15:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市的灯火辉煌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.41,0:15:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样真的没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.87,0:15:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论怎么走…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.67,0:15:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.45,0:15:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.32,0:15:25.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要中止
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  还是信号不好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:34.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话断了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是二人团伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.68,0:15:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个月从你母亲那取钱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并且常去品川宾馆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.53,0:15:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,符合这些条件的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.64,0:15:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有夜长公主的梦乃小姐和公美小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能是那两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.98,0:15:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  如果公美小姐乔装打扮的话的确像男的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.42,0:16:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想让我们这么判断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是海胜却将其他人断定为犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.24,0:16:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是让你有些坐立不安呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.36,0:16:12.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本应沉睡于此的安西惠理其实就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长田安小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长田久子在夜长公主首次登上舞台时
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.55,0:16:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假造出了死于恐怖袭击的第4位架空成员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.49,0:16:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连你那无与伦比的歌声也被利用于此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们分析以后发现
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的声音和安西惠理的声音基本一致
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.12,0:16:34.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同时也与前日被禁止发售的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.73,0:16:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶像程序的追加数据中出现的声音也如出一辙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.69,0:16:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就觉得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么犯人特地将装有被害人的行李箱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.10,0:16:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运送到被害人的家宅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是为了洗脱住在家宅中的人的嫌疑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长田安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:16:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的歌声真的很美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.83,0:17:07.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜长公主的时候我还是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:08.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.70,0:17:12.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为安西惠理录音的事也没有太在意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为每天都能在电视里听到我的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是战争结束后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.86,0:17:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我意识到必须用自己的歌声给
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因战败而一蹶不振的日本打气时
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈却不让我唱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.05,0:17:31.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想成为歌手的我一败涂地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.64,0:17:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想输！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.88,0:17:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾想要相信梦想一定能够实现！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.69,0:17:41.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才在不知名的专辑中出现
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.37,0:17:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以为那样就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.99,0:17:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈说那也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果让别人发现了那是死去的惠理的声音的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.44,0:17:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会带来许多麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.87,0:17:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被掠夺一空
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.66,0:17:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的歌  还有夜长公主  被妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.58,0:18:00.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们永远地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.42,0:18:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沐浴着寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护祷告着的少女们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.89,0:18:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那润湿的双瞳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是最大的罪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.61,0:18:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用爱抚慰勇气之旗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是刚才的人还是打电话来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.48,0:18:34.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拒绝了我成为歌手的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在追捕中的卷荒的尸体被发现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.82,0:18:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是情杀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\frz-90\an5\bord1\be3\3a&H5f\fn@宋体\b1\fs12\3c&H000000&\c&Hffffff&\move(484,182,498,182,0,420)\clip(490,42,577,249)}被害人的情人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因走投无路而自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.14,0:18:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被杀死了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.17,0:18:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是海胜的推理吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.75,0:18:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是卷荒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.63,0:18:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是长田安小姐的歌曲也从此不能出现在这个世界上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.46,0:18:56.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是根据「新情报扩散防止法」的处置
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.69,0:18:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.43,0:19:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话我为什么还要杀死妈妈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.05,0:19:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  坏掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理所当然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.35,0:19:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人总有一天会死去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东西也总有一天会坏掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.56,0:19:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不存在永远不坏的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:15.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然我也会毁坏
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.31,0:19:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不断地在寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.18,0:19:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何要寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.11,0:19:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我还没有伟大到停止寻找还能继续存在下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.02,0:19:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会继续寻找
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.91,0:19:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海胜麟六
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.63,0:19:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖袭击的牺牲者安西惠理的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你们编造的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.55,0:19:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠理的录像也是捏造的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.36,0:19:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜长公主是为了弘扬战意而被制造出来的偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果战后此意图被发现的话可就麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.89,0:19:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你们就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.81,0:19:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.11,0:19:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阴谋论吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.20,0:19:48.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.59,0:19:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家开工
